---
export interface Props {}
---

<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #A00000;
    --background: #f8f6f3;
    --text: #333;
    --accent: #fff;
    --highlight-bg: #fff4f0;
    --table-bg: #fff;
    --table-alt-bg: #fdf2f2;
  }
  .exceptional-section {
    background: var(--background);
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .exceptional-heading {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .narrative-block {
    background: var(--highlight-bg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
  .comparison-container {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .comparison-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .comparison-table th,
  .comparison-table td {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .comparison-table th {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .comparison-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
    background: var(--table-alt-bg);
  }
  .comparison-table tr:nth-child(odd) td {
    background: var(--table-bg);
  }
  .comparison-table td:first-child {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #800000;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .exceptional-heading { font-size: 3.5rem; }
    .narrative-block { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="exceptional-section">
  <h2 class="exceptional-heading">Exceptional Value</h2>

  <div class="narrative-block">
    Picture this: a sleek studio in Dubai, lights humming, cameras rolling, at a price tag that could fund an entire week of shooting in Europe. Now imagine swapping that glare of skyscrapers for the tranquil peaks around Bishkek—same top-tier equipment, same seasoned crew, but with costs trimmed by more than half.
  </div>

  <div class="comparison-container">
    <table class="comparison-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Expense</th>
          <th>Dubai</th>
          <th>Bishkek</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Studio Day Rental</td>
          <td>$5,000</td>
          <td>$1,500</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Camera Package (per day)</td>
          <td>$1,200</td>
          <td>$350</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Crew Rate (pp/day)</td>
          <td>$2,000</td>
          <td>$500</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Post-Production Suite</td>
          <td>$3,000</td>
          <td>$900</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Total Budget</strong></td>
          <td><strong>$100,000</strong></td>
          <td><strong>$40,000</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="narrative-block">
    Those savings aren’t just numbers—they’re extra shooting days, upgraded talent, and creative freedom. In Bishkek, your vision takes front and center, not your overheads.
  </div>

  <div class="cta">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get Your Custom Quote</a>
  </div>
</section>